title: MaxBulk Mailer Pro 8.4.8 + Keygen
description:
MaxBulk Mailer is a full-featured bulk emailer and mail-merge tool for Macintosh and Windows that allows you to send out customized press releases, prices lists and any kind of text or HTML documents to your customers. MaxBulk Mailer is fast, fully customizable and very easy to use. MaxBulk Mailer handles plain text, HTML and styled text documents and gives full support for attachments.

Please, read instructions.txt and follow them to the letter to avoid problems. The application is great. It's just a matter to learn how to use it. Enjoy!
